cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with speech emotion recognition using an end-to-end learning system. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is also a likely category as the paper focuses on speech data and its analysis. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper proposes a novel end-to-end framework for emotion prediction using multi-task learning and attention mechanism. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with developing an intelligent system for emotion recognition from speech. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is a less likely category but still possible as the paper deals with analyzing emotional content in speech data, which can be considered as a form of social network analysis.
